#### "Safe to Bunk" Calculator

```javascript
// How many lectures can student miss and still be at 75%?
function calculateCanMiss(present, total, minRequired = 75) {
  // Formula: present - (minRequired% Ã— total) / (minRequired%)
  // Simplified: How many more absences before dropping below 75%
  
  const requiredPresent = Math.ceil((minRequired / 100) * total);
  const surplus = present - requiredPresent;
  
  return Math.max(0, surplus);  // Can't be negative
}

// Example:
// present = 39, total = 50, minRequired = 75%
// requiredPresent = ceil(0.75 Ã— 50) = 38
// canMiss = 39 - 38 = 1 lecture
```

